{"tid":556154,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人屋企自己開公司/鋪頭？","createTime":"2018-02-10T09:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T19:37:45.000Z","uid":80533,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d973462a142604736813c9797780431502a96e1a","tid":556154,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"無論你係飲食/零售/批發，一齊討論下<br />\n<br />\n我自己好細個6、7歲就被要求去幫手<br />\n放長假=無假<br />\n暑期工都係返自己公司度做<br />\n<br />\n同學以為做太子好好<br />\n生活質數係ok無真係無自由<br />\n畢業唔打算接管生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133e0c2fd21792b7b892d3aebb30bf0d985f96c9","tid":556154,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無論你係飲食/零售/批發，一齊討論下<br />\n<br />\n我自己好細個6、7歲就被要求去幫手<br />\n放長假=無假<br />\n暑期工都係返自己公司度做<br />\n<br />\n同學以為做太子好好<br />\n生活質數係ok<span style=\"color: red;\">但</span>真係無自由<br />\n畢業唔打算接管生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a1a801296061ad381bcc263d01368641f6792cf5","tid":556154,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"無叫我去幫手或接手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ab3781763e4b92ec452707886b62530baec1ae","tid":556154,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1a801296061ad381bcc263d01368641f6792cf5","tid":556154,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"無叫我去幫手或接手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"好幸福<br />\n仲讀緊書定做緊第二行？"},{"pid":"94e7d07df111bea55e15a51bfd97ae2dc8fce910","tid":556154,"uid":121997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:08:30.000Z","msg":"抄樓啦有錢既"},{"pid":"1f6d02b89180a6e029da790c6c63d47271ce5f17","tid":556154,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7ab378