 />\n基本上我都拒絕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為對個個行業冇興趣<br />\n所以基本上完全唔識鋪頭既運作 自己係出面打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想開間自己有興趣既行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b70ce6b3f1059ebc7506ac3b556499d10b96ec","tid":556154,"uid":157858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"細個真係會一放假就比屋企人捉去舖頭<br />\n依家自己出黎做嘢 已經無去好耐"},{"pid":"b0dbd251ece3329be2f83bd5549a1c4c782646be","tid":556154,"uid":164962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"屋企開粥鋪，無理過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ec5ec53a8e232a258984a5278e7204b2c47489","tid":556154,"uid":76003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"屋企開車房<br />\n整重型車<br />\n裝吊機"},{"pid":"6a8f0811dd9ba90cb8169e554379eb2ca91abf6e","tid":556154,"uid":42084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23de32e16d69aa99fa7d0262a204c6a3e734954","tid":556154,"uid":42084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"624b4af861ae6c890e848c0a6dbeb38d98f9a109","tid":556154,"uid":146631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"907c7f200391b79ed54319e750935cb5c1747659","tid":556154,"uid":80533,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"691c6f7ec7cd4b782248a01cd6ad747109b7893e","tid":556154,"uid":146631,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"屋企開車房，細細個已經去車房幫手抹車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：絲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:33:15.000Z","msg":"你係自願定被要求？<br />\n幻想絲打騎住電單車，摸住支棍好有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":